Name:           nss-mdns
Version:        0.14.1
Release:        0
Summary:        Host Name Resolution Via Multicast DNS (Zeroconf) for glibc
License:        LGPL-2.1-or-later
Group:          Productivity/Networking/DNS/Utilities
URL:            https://github.com/lathiat/nss-mdns
